thread.title: 29 Country Songs Haven’t Thought About In 5 Years
thread.title_full: 29 Country Songs You Haven’t Thought About In 5 Years

author: Krista Torres, Farrah Penn
title: 29 Country Songs Haven’t Thought About In 5 Years
text:
Memorable lyrics: “And you throw your head back laughing like a little kid / I think it’s strange that you think I’m funny ‘cause he never did”
ID: 10453209 2. “Red Solo Cup” by Toby Keith youtube.com
Show Dog - Universal Music / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “Red solo cup I fill you up / Let’s have a party”
ID: 10453725 3. “Blown Away” by Carrie Underwood youtube.com
Artista Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “Shatter every window till it’s all blown away / Every brick / Every board / Every slamming door blown away”
ID: 10453748 4. “5-1-5-0” by Dierks Bentley youtube.com
Capitol Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “5-1-5-0 / Somebody call the po-po”
ID: 10453763 5. “Springsteen” by Eric Church youtube.com
EMI Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “When I think about you / I think about 17”
ID: 10454434 6. “Over You” by Miranda Lambert youtube.com
RCA Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “But you went away / How dare you / I miss you / They say I’ll be OK / But I’m not going to ever get over you”
ID: 10454446 7. “Wanted” by Hunter Hayes youtube.com
Atlantic / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “‘Cause I wanna wrap you up / Wanna kiss your lips / I wanna make you feel wanted”
ID: 10454506 8. “Drunk On You” by Luke Bryan youtube.com
Capitol Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “Hey, I’m a little drunk on you / And high on summertime”
ID: 10454456 9. “How Country Feels” by Randy Houser youtube.com
Stoney Creek / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “I’ll take you up and down these hollers and hills / Let me show you how country feels”
ID: 10454646 10. “Home” by Dierks Bentley youtube.com
Capitol Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “But this is still the place that we all call home”
ID: 10453925 11. “Kissed You Goodnight” by Gloriana youtube.com
Emblem/Warner Bros. Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “And now that I’ve kissed you / It’s a good night / Good night / Baby, goodnight”
ID: 10454427 12. “Even if it Breaks Your Heart” by Eli Young Band youtube.com
Republic Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “ h, I can hear em playin’ / I can hear the ringin’ of a beat up ol’ guitar / h, I can hear em singin / ‘Keep on dreamin’ even if it breaks your heart’”
ID: 10454415 13. “Time is Love” by Josh Turner youtube.com
MCA Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “Time is love / Gotta run / Love to hang longer but I got someone”
ID: 10453945 14. “Red” by Taylor Swift youtube.com
Big Machine Records / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “Loving him is like driving a new Maserati down a dead-end street”
ID: 10454572 15. “True Believers” by Darius Rucker youtube.com
Capitol Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “We are two / True believers”
ID: 10454665 16. “You Don’t Know Her Like I Do” by Brantley Gilbert youtube.com
Average Joes / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “‘Cause you don’t know her like I do / You’ll never understand / You don’t know what we’ve been through / That girl’s my best friend”
ID: 10454378 17. “Why Ya Wanna” by Jana Kramer youtube.com
Elektra Records / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “Why ya gotta / Why ya wanna / Make me keep wantin’ you”
ID: 10454393 18. “Cowboys and Angels” by Dustin Lynch youtube.com
Broken Bow / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “There’s a want and there’s a need / There’s a history between girls like her and guys like me / Cowboys and angels”
ID: 10454405 19. “Somethin’ Bout a Truck” by Kip Moore youtube.com
MCA Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “Somethin’ ‘bout a truck in a farmer’s field / A no trespass sign and time to kill / Nobody’s gonna get hurt / So what’s the big deal?”
ID: 10454470 20. “A Woman Like You” by Lee Brice youtube.com
Curb / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “But if I was a single man / Alone and out there on the loose / Well I’d be looking for a woman like you”
ID: 10454486 21. “All Your Life” by The Band Perry youtube.com
Republic Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “I don’t want the whole world / The sun, the moon and all their light / I just wanna be the only girl / You love all your life”
ID: 10454514 22. “Pontoon” by Little Big Town youtube.com
Capitol Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “On the pontoon / Makin’ waves and catchin’ rays up on the roof / Jumpin’ out the back / Don’t act like you don’t want to / Party in slow motion / Out here in the open, mm, motorboatin’”
ID: 10454526 23. “I’m Gonna Love You Through It” by Martina McBride youtube.com
Republic Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: When you feel lost and scared to death / Like you can’t take one more step / Just take my hand / Together we can do it / I’m gonna love you through it”
ID: 10454536 24. “Beer Money” by Kip Moore youtube.com
MCA Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “You got the kiss that tastes like honey / And I got a little beer money”
ID: 10454553 25. “The Trouble With Girls” by Scotty McCreery youtube.com
Mercury Nashville, 19 / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “Yeah, the trouble with girls / Is nobody loves trouble as much as me”
ID: 10454610 26. “Baggage Claim ” by Miranda Lambert youtube.com
RCA Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “At the baggage claim / You got a lot of luggage in your name”
ID: 10454618 27. “God Gave Me You” by Blake Shelton youtube.com
Warner Bros. Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “‘Cause God gave me you for the ups and downs / God gave me you for the days of doubt / For when I think I’ve lost my way / There are no words here left to say, it’s true / God gave me you”
ID: 10454630 28. “Drink In My Hand” by Eric Church youtube.com
EMI Nashville / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “No need to complicate it / I’m a simple man / All you got to do is put a drink in my hand”
ID: 10454655 29. “Fly Over States” by Jason Aldean youtube.com
Broken Bow / Via Wikipedia
 Memorable lyrics: “A couple guys in first class on a flight from New York to Los Angeles / Kinda making small talk killing time / Flirting with the flight attendants / 30,000 feet above could be Oklahoma”
